Bugs, skips, glitches, strategies, tools:
Speedrun discord server: https://discord.com/invite/HvmjYqZb4f
If you want to get world record play eather on 1.0.5 or 1.0.4. 1.0.5 is recommended since more recent.
Microwave: https://youtu.be/qZs_ywQcbO8?si=8kP9VCQ5JnAmVEZD
Day1 mail: https://imgur.com/a/AkO2y0G Just aim at that place exactly and click E. Only works on day1. 
Use mercy ending to get faster times.
Timer: https://livesplit.org/downloads/
Platform to upload speedruns: https://www.speedrun.com/TheSalesman, youtube, any other social media where it doesn't get deleted. If using twitch: Twitch VODs are not allowed, but Twitch Highlights are. However, it is your responsibility to ensure those highlights never get deleted.
To record you can just use built in tools like for Windows: snipping tool, for Linux: Ctrl + Alt + Shift + R shuld work on most distributions. 
The door skip:When u are to far away from a door it closes but past the to-far-away-point u can still close the front door which means it stays open bc of text u cant interact with stuff but with this  u can prepare
Nebula video script about skips and stuff https://docs.google.com/document/d/1xfv5PFk0Y32i7kvHk2vNaIBnD5vu0W4KRH8dY4JduS0/edit?usp=sharing
The last version this works on is 1.0.5 On day 6 when you wake up you can immediately go out the door and go to the trashcan and trow away trash that you don't have. Then just go back to the door and you just skipped day 6.
